Tools and Trick for Embedded Linux
==================================
1. grep -nrwI "string-need-find" <path-need-search>
2. grep -nrwI --include=*\.c --include=*\.h "string-need-find" <path-need-search>
3. find <path-need-search> -name "file-name"
4. dump_stack();
5. pr_emerg("Dungnt98 %s, %d", __func__, __LINE__);